[
    {
        "text": "(flames crackling)",
        "start": 0.255,
        "duration": 2.189
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat blues music)",
        "start": 2.444,
        "duration": 3.4
    },
    {
        "text": "♪ I'm going down to the house of sausage ♪",
        "start": 5.844,
        "duration": 3.324
    },
    {
        "text": "- [Narrator] Welcome to BBQPitBoys.com.",
        "start": 9.168,
        "duration": 2.914
    },
    {
        "text": "Today we're cooking up some",
        "start": 12.082,
        "duration": 1.161
    },
    {
        "text": "smoked bacon cheeseburgers on the grill.",
        "start": 13.243,
        "duration": 2.646
    },
    {
        "text": "And they're real easy to do.",
        "start": 15.889,
        "duration": 2.163
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, here I've\ngot some quality bacon,",
        "start": 18.052,
        "duration": 3.124
    },
    {
        "text": "it's a thick-cut bacon.",
        "start": 21.176,
        "duration": 1.63
    },
    {
        "text": "You wanna use a good bacon",
        "start": 22.806,
        "duration": 1.753
    },
    {
        "text": "any time you're making up some\ncheeseburgers on the grill.",
        "start": 24.559,
        "duration": 3.47
    },
    {
        "text": "What we're gonna do with it here first,",
        "start": 28.029,
        "duration": 1.722
    },
    {
        "text": "we're gonna take it and\nwe're gonna put it indirect",
        "start": 29.751,
        "duration": 2.518
    },
    {
        "text": "here on a kettle grill,",
        "start": 32.269,
        "duration": 1.666
    },
    {
        "text": "'cause we're gonna low\nand slow this bacon, man.",
        "start": 33.935,
        "duration": 3.056
    },
    {
        "text": "It's gonna take about an hour,",
        "start": 36.991,
        "duration": 1.285
    },
    {
        "text": "maybe an hour and a half, or two.",
        "start": 38.276,
        "duration": 2.097
    },
    {
        "text": "Wanna do it low and slow.",
        "start": 40.373,
        "duration": 2.303
    },
    {
        "text": "So what you do here, is the pound,",
        "start": 42.676,
        "duration": 1.222
    },
    {
        "text": "you spread out those slices",
        "start": 43.898,
        "duration": 1.547
    },
    {
        "text": "and that's pork belly bacon right there.",
        "start": 45.445,
        "duration": 2.533
    },
    {
        "text": "Low and slow it.",
        "start": 47.978,
        "duration": 1.333
    },
    {
        "text": "And this is what you got,\nabout, maybe an hour,",
        "start": 51.389,
        "duration": 2.479
    },
    {
        "text": "hour and 15 minutes\ninto this low and slow.",
        "start": 53.868,
        "duration": 3.212
    },
    {
        "text": "You can see that bacon's\nlooking real good.",
        "start": 57.08,
        "duration": 4.183
    },
    {
        "text": "And through the miracle of time,",
        "start": 61.263,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "we've smoked up this bacon.",
        "start": 63.073,
        "duration": 2.278
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh yeah (chuckles).",
        "start": 65.351,
        "duration": 2.705
    },
    {
        "text": "If you've never done this\nbefore, you gotta check this out.",
        "start": 68.056,
        "duration": 3.718
    },
    {
        "text": "All right now, I've chopped\nthe bacon up in small pieces",
        "start": 71.774,
        "duration": 3.347
    },
    {
        "text": "and here I've got some ground chuck,",
        "start": 75.121,
        "duration": 2.272
    },
    {
        "text": "I've got some chopped onion,\nwe've got some cheese.",
        "start": 77.393,
        "duration": 2.029
    },
    {
        "text": "And let me put this together here.",
        "start": 79.422,
        "duration": 1.989
    },
    {
        "text": "That's about, maybe five\npounds of ground chuck,",
        "start": 81.411,
        "duration": 3.466
    },
    {
        "text": "put in about a cup of\nchopped onion in there,",
        "start": 84.877,
        "duration": 4.152
    },
    {
        "text": "and here we've got about\na pound of chopped bacon,",
        "start": 89.029,
        "duration": 3.328
    },
    {
        "text": "that smoked bacon.",
        "start": 92.357,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "And here I'm gonna add\nabout a cup of cheese.",
        "start": 95.377,
        "duration": 4.365
    },
    {
        "text": "I think you know where\nwe're going with this.",
        "start": 99.742,
        "duration": 3.513
    },
    {
        "text": "All you need to add there, is\na little more black pepper.",
        "start": 103.255,
        "duration": 2.541
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 105.796,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "There's plenty of salt in\nthere already with the bacon.",
        "start": 108.875,
        "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
        "text": "All right now give it a good mix.",
        "start": 111.575,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "Blend it all up.",
        "start": 116.692,
        "duration": 1.333
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh baby (chuckles) oh yeah.",
        "start": 119.938,
        "duration": 4.072
    },
    {
        "text": "Give it a good mix.",
        "start": 124.01,
        "duration": 1.583
    },
    {
        "text": "Man.",
        "start": 127.634,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "That's good enough to eat\nalready, if you know what I mean.",
        "start": 130.88,
        "duration": 4.167
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, that ground\nchuck has been mixed.",
        "start": 136.664,
        "duration": 3.667
    },
    {
        "text": "Nothing left to do now but,",
        "start": 141.356,
        "duration": 1.996
    },
    {
        "text": "we're gonna make some patties.",
        "start": 143.352,
        "duration": 1.155
    },
    {
        "text": "Now we're gonna make about 3/4 pound",
        "start": 144.507,
        "duration": 2.851
    },
    {
        "text": "to one pound patties here.",
        "start": 147.358,
        "duration": 2.167
    },
    {
        "text": "(bowl clanks)",
        "start": 150.997,
        "duration": 2.261
    },
    {
        "text": "If you've never formed a good\nburger, this is how you do it.",
        "start": 153.258,
        "duration": 2.467
    },
    {
        "text": "You're gonna compress it pretty tight.",
        "start": 155.725,
        "duration": 2.894
    },
    {
        "text": "It'll hold together while\nyou got it on the grill.",
        "start": 158.619,
        "duration": 4.034
    },
    {
        "text": "Man.",
        "start": 162.653,
        "duration": 1.426
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat rock music)",
        "start": 164.079,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "There's nothing like\nsmoked bacon cheeseburgers",
        "start": 169.28,
        "duration": 2.208
    },
    {
        "text": "on the grill.",
        "start": 171.488,
        "duration": 1.121
    },
    {
        "text": "Like I said, you gotta\ncheck this out, man.",
        "start": 172.609,
        "duration": 3.583
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, let's push this along.",
        "start": 177.239,
        "duration": 2.186
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat rock music)",
        "start": 179.425,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, those patties have been made.",
        "start": 187.29,
        "duration": 3.769
    },
    {
        "text": "Uh, look at that, with the onion,",
        "start": 191.059,
        "duration": 2.587
    },
    {
        "text": "the smoked bacon in there,\nsome cheese, oh yeah.",
        "start": 193.646,
        "duration": 4.723
    },
    {
        "text": "Now what we're gonna do, is\nwe're gonna put it on the grill.",
        "start": 198.369,
        "duration": 4.167
    },
    {
        "text": "We're gonna sear it\ndirectly first, each side.",
        "start": 203.687,
        "duration": 3.738
    },
    {
        "text": "You know all about that if\nyou've been watching us.",
        "start": 207.425,
        "duration": 4.236
    },
    {
        "text": "These are fairly thick burgers here",
        "start": 211.661,
        "duration": 1.881
    },
    {
        "text": "so we're gonna use this\ntechnique over medium heat.",
        "start": 213.542,
        "duration": 3.143
    },
    {
        "text": "(barbecue sizzles)",
        "start": 216.685,
        "duration": 3.683
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh man.",
        "start": 220.368,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you smell that?",
        "start": 223.774,
        "duration": 2.139
    },
    {
        "text": "It smells good.",
        "start": 225.913,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat rock music)",
        "start": 227.953,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, these burgers have been seared.",
        "start": 233.213,
        "duration": 3.5
    },
    {
        "text": "The trick here is move 'em indirect,",
        "start": 237.836,
        "duration": 1.862
    },
    {
        "text": "opposite the hot coals,",
        "start": 239.698,
        "duration": 1.222
    },
    {
        "text": "'cause we don't want 'em burnt.",
        "start": 240.92,
        "duration": 2.418
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat rock music)",
        "start": 243.338,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh yeah.",
        "start": 249.955,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Could've moved this video\nalong a little bit faster, but",
        "start": 252.143,
        "duration": 4.167
    },
    {
        "text": "kinda like doing this.",
        "start": 258.209,
        "duration": 2.252
    },
    {
        "text": "Put the cover on, we're\ngonna cook 'em to about",
        "start": 260.461,
        "duration": 4.543
    },
    {
        "text": "medium-rare or medium.",
        "start": 265.004,
        "duration": 1.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Or you cook 'em well-done,\nthe way you like.",
        "start": 267.799,
        "duration": 3.667
    },
    {
        "text": "And through the miracle of time,",
        "start": 273.584,
        "duration": 2.601
    },
    {
        "text": "these burgers are just about done",
        "start": 276.185,
        "duration": 2.077
    },
    {
        "text": "and what we're gonna do here",
        "start": 278.262,
        "duration": 1.253
    },
    {
        "text": "is we're gonna take some\nof this shredded cheese",
        "start": 279.515,
        "duration": 2.215
    },
    {
        "text": "and we're gonna put 'em on\na couple of these burgers",
        "start": 281.73,
        "duration": 3.628
    },
    {
        "text": "and fix 'em up the way you want.",
        "start": 285.358,
        "duration": 2.123
    },
    {
        "text": "Some more onion, maybe mushroom.",
        "start": 287.481,
        "duration": 2.667
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh yeah.",
        "start": 291.268,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, I'd say it's time to eat.",
        "start": 295.417,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Take 'em off the grill.",
        "start": 301.213,
        "duration": 2.364
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat rock music)",
        "start": 303.577,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I'll take a cheeseburger.",
        "start": 308.937,
        "duration": 2.083
    },
    {
        "text": "Sometimes, just a simple\nbarbecue like that",
        "start": 314.844,
        "duration": 2.225
    },
    {
        "text": "is all you need.",
        "start": 317.069,
        "duration": 1.557
    },
    {
        "text": "Now I know a lot of you\nknow how to make burgers,",
        "start": 318.626,
        "duration": 3.048
    },
    {
        "text": "if you haven't done it this way,",
        "start": 321.674,
        "duration": 1.891
    },
    {
        "text": "phew, you gotta give it a try, all right?",
        "start": 323.565,
        "duration": 3.464
    },
    {
        "text": "Throw some more bacon on there.",
        "start": 327.029,
        "duration": 2.251
    },
    {
        "text": "And a big, fat slice of Vidalia onion.",
        "start": 329.28,
        "duration": 3.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Just a shot of chuck.",
        "start": 333.24,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "Whatever your favorite condiments are.",
        "start": 336.864,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "And as always, we apologize,",
        "start": 340.764,
        "duration": 2.413
    },
    {
        "text": "oh yeah, for eating in\nfront of you like this.",
        "start": 343.177,
        "duration": 4.63
    },
    {
        "text": "That's pitmaster privy .",
        "start": 347.807,
        "duration": 2.081
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat rock music)",
        "start": 349.888,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So the next time you're\nlooking for a burger recipe",
        "start": 357.141,
        "duration": 2.643
    },
    {
        "text": "for your barbecue,",
        "start": 359.784,
        "duration": 2.083
    },
    {
        "text": "you check out BBQPitBoys.com.",
        "start": 361.867,
        "duration": 2.417
    },
    {
        "text": "(heavy rock music)",
        "start": 365.414,
        "duration": 2.917
    },
    {
        "text": "(crow cawing)",
        "start": 371.13,
        "duration": 2.5
    }
]